         <abstract>
            <p>
               The name of the scribe written down. Sometimes the purpose of such a signature is not clear (just a pen trial?). 
            </p>
            <p>An example is:
            <ref type="mss" corresp="ESdd"/>, f. 2v:
               <foreign xml:lang="gez">መምረይ᎓ ገብረ᎓ ጻድቅ᎓ እቃቤት። ዛቲ᎓ መጽሐፍ᎓ ዘጸሐፍዋ᎓ ሰርጸ᎓ ሚካኤል᎓ አሜን᎓ መምህርነ᎓ ዘዮሐንስ ይባርክ᎓ አሜን᎓ ለይኩን።</foreign></p>
